style.show:
Bubble style: {style}
Bubble position: {position}
Show rarity: {showRarity}
Bubble width: {width}
Bubble margin: {margin}
Shiny rainbow: {rainbow}
Use /buddy style <classic|round>, /buddy position <top|left>, /buddy rarity <on|off>, /buddy width <10-60>, /buddy margin <0-20>, /buddy rainbow [<#hex>...] to change.

